<form>
  <input type="hidden" name="typeof-investor" value="enterprise" />
  <input id="enterprise-legal-form" type="hidden" name="legal_form" value="" />

  <div id="enterprise-provable-menu" class="payment-sub-option">
      <h3 class="text-center">La Ley considera empresa de gran activo aquella que reúna al menos dos de estas tres características. Por favor, marque las casillas correspondientes.</h3>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">

          <label for="check-1" class="check-auth checkbox-inline">
              <input type="checkbox" name="check-1" id="check-1" value="1">
              El total de las partidas de su activo es igual o superior a 1 millón de euros.
          </label>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">

          <label for="check-2" class="check-auth checkbox-inline">
              <input type="checkbox" name="check-2" id="check-2" value="1">
              El importe de su cifra anual de negocios es igual o superior a 2 millones de euros.
          </label>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">

          <label for="check-3" class="check-auth checkbox-inline">
              <input type="checkbox" name="check-3" id="check-3" value="1">
              Sus recursos propios son iguales o superiores a 300.000 euros.
          </label>

      </div>
  </div>

  <div id="enterprise-profesional-disclaimer" class="enterprise-disclaimer">
      <p>Por favor, escoja la categoría de inversor profesional a la pertenece, según el artículo 78 bis 3 de la Ley 24/1988 del Mercado de Valores.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="enterprise-others-disclaimer" class="enterprise-disclaimer">
      <p>La Bolsa Social le considera inversor no acreditado y no podrá invertir más de 3.000 € en este proyecto.</p>
      <p>(Si desea invertir más de 3.000 €, por favor póngase en contacto con nosotros a través de <a href="mailto:acreditacion@bolsasocial.com">acreditacion@bolsasocial.com</a>. Se le pedirá que cumplimente un cuestionario de idoneidad y nos remita documentos acreditativos)</p>
  </div>

  <div id="type-of-investor-group" class="form-group">
      <label for="type-of-investor" class="pull-left">
        <span class="label-text">Tipo de empresa acreditada:</span>
      </label>
      <div class="form-control-wrap">
        <select class="form-control form-control-inline" id="type-of-investor" name="e_type" required>
          <option value="" disabled selected>Select one</option>
          <option value="CUSTOM">Otro</option>
        </select>
      </div>
  </div>



  <div id="enterprise-form">

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="enterprise-name" class="pull-left">
        <span class="label-text">Razón social:</span>
      </label>
      <label for="enterprise-name" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
      <div class="form-control-wrap">
        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-name" name="business_name" required minlength="3" maxlength="40" value="" placeholder="Razón Social">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="cif" class="pull-left">
            <span class="label-text">Cif:</span>
          </label>
          <label for="cif" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
          <div class="form-control-wrap">
            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="cif" name="e_id_number" maxlength="20" required value="" placeholder="XXXXXXXX">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-7">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="type-of-enterprise" class="pull-left">
            <span class="label-text">Tipo de persona jurídica:</span>
          </label>
          <div class="form-control-wrap">
            <select class="form-control form-control-inline" id="type-of-enterprise" name="e_type" required>
              <option value="" disabled selected>Select one</option>
              <option value="S.EN.C.POR.A.">Sociedad Comanditaria por Acciones</option>
              <option value="CUSTOM">Otro</option>
            </select>
            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="custom-type-of-enterprise" name="e_custom_type" minlength="2" maxlength="50" required value="" placeholder="Escribe aquí el tipo de persona jurídica">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="enterprise-form-name" class="pull-left">
        <span class="label-text">Nombre:</span>
      </label>
      <label for="enterprise-form-name" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
      <div class="form-control-wrap">
        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-name" name="name" minlength="2" maxlength="60" required value="" placeholder="Escribe aquí tu nombre">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="enterprise-form-surname" class="pull-left">
        <span class="label-text">Apellido:</span>
      </label>
      <label for="enterprise-form-surname" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
      <div class="form-control-wrap">
        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-surname" name="surname" minlength="2" maxlength="60" required value="" placeholder="Escribe aquí tus apellidos">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="occupation" class="pull-left">
            <span class="label-text">Cargo en la empresa:</span>
          </label>
          <label for="occupation" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
          <div class="form-control-wrap">
            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="occupation" name="job" minlength="2" maxlength="32" required value="" placeholder="Cargo en la empresa">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 checkbox">
        <label for="check-enterprise-auth" class="check-auth checkbox-inline">
            <input type="checkbox" name="check-enterprise-auth" required="" id="check-enterprise-auth" value="1"> 
            Tengo capacidad legal para comprometer la inversión en nombre de la entidad.
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="enterprise-form-phone" class="pull-left">
            <span class="label-text">Teléfono:</span>
          </label>
          <label for="enterprise-form-phone" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
          <div class="form-control-wrap">
            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-phone" name="e_phone" minlength="9" maxlength="16" required value="" placeholder="+34 XXXXXXXXX">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-6">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="enterprise-form-nationality" class="pull-left">
            <span class="label-text">Nacionalidad:</span>
          </label>
          <div class="form-control-wrap">
            <select class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-nationality" name="e_nationality" required>
              <option value="86">Islas Georgias del Sur y Sandwich del Sur</option>
              <option value="196">Senegal</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-address" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">Dirección:</span>
        </label>
        <label for="enterprise-form-address" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-address" name="e_address" minlength="5" maxlength="255" required value="" placeholder="C/ ...">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-addressNum" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">Número:</span>
        </label>
        <label for="enterprise-form-addressNum" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-addressNum" name="e_address_num" minlength="1" maxlength="10" required value="" placeholder="XX">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-5">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-postcode" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">Código postal:</span>
        </label>
        <label for="enterprise-form-postcode" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-postcode" name="e_postcode" minlength="5" maxlength="10" required value="" placeholder="XXXXX">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-city" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">Ciudad:</span>
        </label>
        <label for="enterprise-form-city" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-city" name="e_city" minlength="2" maxlength="50" required value="" placeholder="">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-6">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-province" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">Provincia:</span>
        </label>
        <label for="enterprise-form-province" class="pull-right"><span class="btn btn-link btn-edit">Editar</span></label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-province" name="e_state" minlength="2" maxlength="50" required value="" placeholder="">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="enterprise-form-country" class="pull-left">
          <span class="label-text">País:</span>
        </label>
        <div class="form-control-wrap">
          <select class="form-control form-control-inline" id="enterprise-form-country" name="e_country" required>
            <option value="86">Islas Georgias del Sur y Sandwich del Sur</option>
            <option value="196">Senegal</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</form>